      <title>警方在驱散令后拆除了加州大学洛杉矶分校的抗议营地</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-02/tensions-high-at-ucla-as-protesters-ordered-to-disperse</link>
      <description><![CDATA[前一天晚上与反抗议者发生暴力事件后，身着防暴装备的警察拆除了亲巴勒斯坦抗议者在洛杉矶加州大学搭建的路障和帐篷。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-02/tensions-high-at-ucla-as-protesters-ordered-to-disperse</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 08:45:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登称盟友日本与中国、俄罗斯一样“仇外”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-02/biden-now-calls-ally-japan-xenophobic-along-with-china-russia</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统乔·拜登在华盛顿举行的竞选筹款活动上发表讲话时，将盟友日本以及竞争对手中国和俄罗斯列入他所谓的“仇外”国家名单。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-02/biden-now-calls-ally-japan-xenophobic-along-with-china-russia</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 01:00:02 GMT</pubDate>
